name: WHAT WOULD HAPPEN IF WE REACHED THE EDGE OF THE COSMOS AND SAW OURSELVES PEERING AT OURSELVES?
description: Think about that for a second...what if we were at the edge? I know, I know...there is no edge of the universe and everywhere is the center, but as a thought exercise it would crazy if somehow, someway to reach the very edge of it and see ourselves looking at ourselves. What would happen if we reached out to touch? Would we be touching ourselves? Would it be real? Would it be a hologram or an illusion? Uhhhh..you might want to lay off those edibles Andrew for a bit. How is this art? As a conceptual artist, my job is to have you use your mind. The art is in your head already, I'm just presenting the words to bring them out of your mind.
